Four 30-minute episodes.

4
00:00:09,642 --> 00:00:11,211
-Four episodes?
-That long?

5
00:00:11,277 --> 00:00:12,746
Two hours?!

6
00:00:12,812 --> 00:00:14,280
-Nothing'll happen.
-Yeah.

7
00:00:14,347 --> 00:00:16,383
There won't be any incidents.

8
00:00:16,449 --> 00:00:17,817
It's so peaceful.

9
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:20,587
-Should we fight?
-Okay.

10
00:00:20,653 --> 00:00:21,721
Hey, you!

11
00:00:22,389 --> 00:00:24,958
-Not young enough to fight.
-Boring, right?

12
00:00:25,458 --> 00:00:26,559
Nothing.

13
00:00:26,626 --> 00:00:28,161
There must be something.

14
00:00:28,228 --> 00:00:31,364
No, we've already done all that
in the last 25 years.

15
00:00:31,898 --> 00:00:33,767
How long are you gonna stay?

16
00:00:33,833 --> 00:00:35,535
Until November 1.

17
00:00:35,602 --> 00:00:38,104
Oh, nothing will happen.

18
00:01:04,531 --> 00:01:07,534
<i>This is documentary series</i> RIDE ON TIME.

19
