{\an8}1995 NOVEMBER 1 DEBUT

20
00:01:15,508 --> 00:01:22,482
{\an8}"WA NI NATTE ODOROU"

21
00:01:27,954 --> 00:01:34,928
"AI NANDA"

22
00:01:53,546 --> 00:01:55,882
